http://www.king-foo.com/2011/11/creating-debianubuntu-deb-packages/

build with :  dpkg-deb --build bluesky-zmq
install with sudo dkpg -i bluesky-zmq.deb

if you get dependency errors, after running that command, run:
sudo apt-get -f install

then run command again:
install with sudo dkpg -i bluesky-zmq.deb
